{"title":"Listener使用","date":"2019-03-29T09:04:21.000Z","link":"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener","comments":true,"tags":["Java Web"],"categories":["Java Web"],"updated":"2019-10-24T07:38:40.709Z","content":"<p>Listener的基本使用记录</p>\n  <a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"Listener的使用\">Listener的使用<a href=\"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener#Listener的使用\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"概念\">概念<a href=\"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener#概念\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li><p>一些基本的概念</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>事件： 一件事件， </p>\n<p>事件源： 事件发生的地方</p>\n<p>监听器： 实际上就是一个对象</p>\n<p>注册监听： 将事件， 事件源 ， 监听器绑定到一起，当事件源上发生某种事件后，执行监听器。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>事件的监听的机制</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>接口回调</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>作用</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>监听某一个事件的发生,状态的改变。</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"监听器使用\">监听器使用<a href=\"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener#监听器使用\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li><p>步骤</p>\n<ol>\n<li>实现ServletContextListener接口</li>\n<li>复写方法</li>\n<li>完成配置文件 可以通过注释方法 或者配置xml文件</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"监听器三种分类使用\">监听器三种分类使用<a href=\"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener#监听器三种分类使用\"></a></h3><h4 id=\"监听三个作用域的的创建和销毁\">监听三个作用域的的创建和销毁<a href=\"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener#监听三个作用域的的创建和销毁\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li><p>对象的作用域</p>\n<p>request  —httpServletRequest<br>session  —httpSession<br>aapplication  — ServletContext</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>ServletContextListener</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>servletcontext创建：启动服务器的时候</p>\n<p>servletContext销毁：关闭服务器. 从服务器移除项目</p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li><p>ServletRequestListener</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>request创建:</p>\n<p>访问服务器上的任意资源都会有请求出现。</p>\n<p>访问 html： 会<br>访问 jsp:    会<br>访问 servlet : 会 </p>\n<p>request销毁：</p>\n<p>服务器已经对这次请求作出了响应</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>​      代码实现：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">MyRequestListener</span> <span class=\"keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"title\">ServletRequestListener</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"meta\">@Override</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">requestDestroyed</span><span class=\"params\">(ServletRequestEvent sre)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"servletrequest 销毁了\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"meta\">@Override</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">requestInitialized</span><span class=\"params\">(ServletRequestEvent sre)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"servletrequest 初始化了\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><p>HttpSessionListener</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>session的创建</p>\n<pre><code>只要调用getSession\n</code></pre><p>​    html:        不会<br>​    jsp:        会      getSession();<br>​    servlet:     会</p>\n<p>session的销毁:</p>\n<pre><code>超时  30分钟\n</code></pre><p>​    非正常关闭 销毁</p>\n<p>​    正常关闭服务器(序列化)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>​    代码实现</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">MySessionListener</span> <span class=\"keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"title\">HttpSessionListener</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"meta\">@Override</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">sessionCreated</span><span class=\"params\">(HttpSessionEvent se)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"创建session了\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"meta\">@Override</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">sessionDestroyed</span><span class=\"params\">(HttpSessionEvent se)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"销毁session了\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"监听三个作用域属性状态变更\">监听三个作用域属性状态变更<a href=\"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener#监听三个作用域属性状态变更\"></a></h4><blockquote>\n<p>可以监听在作用域中值 添加  | 替换  | 移除的动作。 </p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>servletContext — ServletContextAttributeListener</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener/1.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>request — ServletRequestAttributeListener</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener/2.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>session — HttpSessionAttributeListener</p>\n<p><img src=\"/2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener/3.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"监听httpSession里面存值的状态变更\">监听httpSession里面存值的状态变更<a href=\"2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener#监听httpSession里面存值的状态变更\"></a></h4><blockquote>\n<p>这一类的监听器不用注册</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><p>HttpSessionBindingListener</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//监听对象与session 绑定和解除绑定 的动作\t 让javaBean 实现该接口即可</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"meta\">@Override</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">valueBound</span><span class=\"params\">(HttpSessionBindingEvent event)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"对象被绑定进来了\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"meta\">@Override</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">valueUnbound</span><span class=\"params\">(HttpSessionBindingEvent event)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"对象被解除绑定\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>HttpSessionActivationListener</p>\n<p>作用：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>用于监听现在session的值 是 钝化 （序列化）还是活化 （反序列化）的动作</p>\n<p>钝化 （序列化） : 把内存中的数据 存储到硬盘上</p>\n<p>活化 （反序列化）: 把硬盘中的数据读取到内存中。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>意义</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>session中的值可能会很多， 并且我们有很长一段时间不使用这个内存中的值， 那么可以考虑把session的值可以存储到硬盘上(钝化)，等下一次在使用的时候，在从硬盘上提取出来。 (活化)</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>配置方法</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>在tomcat里面 conf/context.xml 里面配置</p>\n<pre><code>对所有的运行在这个服务器的项目生效  \n</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>在conf/Catalina/localhost/context.xml 配置</p>\n<p> 对 localhost生效。  localhost:8080</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在自己的web工程项目中的 META-INF/context.xml    只对当前的工程生效。</p>\n <figure class=\"highlight xml\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">maxIdleSwap ： 1分钟不用就钝化</span><br><span class=\"line\">directory ：  钝化后的那个文件存放的目录位置。 </span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">\tD:\\tomcat\\apache-tomcat-7.0.52\\work\\Catalina\\localhost\\ListenerDemo\\itheima</span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">Context</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">Manager</span> <span class=\"attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"org.apache.catalina.session.PersistentManager\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">maxIdleSwap</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"1\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">Store</span> <span class=\"attr\">className</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"org.apache.catalina.session.FileStore\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">directory</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"itheima\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">Manager</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">Context</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"IDEA配置javaweb项目","link":"2019/04/01/Java Web/Configuration of java web in IDEA"},"next":{"title":"JSTL使用","link":"2019/03/29/Java Web/JSTL"},"plink":"http://www.zqynn.cn/2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener/","toc":[{"title":"Listener的使用","id":"Listener的使用","index":"1","children":[{"title":"概念","id":"概念","index":"1.1"},{"title":"监听器使用","id":"监听器使用","index":"1.2"},{"title":"监听器三种分类使用","id":"监听器三种分类使用","index":"1.3","children":[{"title":"监听三个作用域的的创建和销毁","id":"监听三个作用域的的创建和销毁","index":"1.3.1"},{"title":"监听三个作用域属性状态变更","id":"监听三个作用域属性状态变更","index":"1.3.2"},{"title":"监听httpSession里面存值的状态变更","id":"监听httpSession里面存值的状态变更","index":"1.3.3"}]}]}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://www.zqynn.cn/2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener/\" title=\"Listener使用\">http://www.zqynn.cn/2019/03/29/Java Web/Listener/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}